<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
 
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
 
  .gif-container {
            position: fixed;
            top: 65%; /* Adjust the distance from the bottom */
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            max-width: 230px; /* Adjust the size of the gif container */
            max-height: 230px; /* Adjust the size of the gif container */
            margin: 0 4% 4% 0; /* Adjust the margin */
        }
 
        .gif-container img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 10px; /* Adjust the border-radius for a rounded look */
        }
        h1 {
            margin: 4%;
        }
 
        .content-container {
            background: white;
            margin: 4%;
            padding: 4%;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            z-index: 1; /* Ensure it's below the gif container */
            position: relative;
        }
    </style>
    <title>About Us</title>
</head>
 
<body>
 
    <h1>About us</h1>
 
    <div class="content-container">
        <ul class="fs-5">
            <li>At Food Bank, we help donors provide food to those who need it across the country.</li>
            <li>Our main aim is to help others and spread joy by drawing smiles on people's faces.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
 
    <div class="gif-container">
        <img src="/assets/images/fruits111-unscreen.gif" alt="gif">
    </div>
 
</body>
 
</html>